body.description: Make organization fun and easy with the BIC Brite Liner Grip Pastel Highlighters Set. These thin highlighters have a versatile chisel tip that creates fine and broad lines. BIC’s highlighter markers feature translucent ink that emphasizes what’s important on the page without obscuring the text below. They’re ideal for use on textbooks, notebooks, documents and more. Each highlighters pen can write for up to eight hours without a cap and not dry out, so you can work with confidence. BIC Brite Liner Grip chisel-tip highlighters fit snugly in your hand and have a soft grip for added comfort and control. These trendy highlighters make great gifts for teens or creatives of all ages.Looking for cute highlighters for journals or stylish marker sets for adults? BIC Brite Liner Pastel Highlighters add a fun pop of color to your art, office or school supplies. Each highlighters pack contains 12 chisel tip markers, with two in each of the following six colors: Orange, Yellow, Green, Blue, Purple and Pink. BIC multicolor highlighters are non-toxic and ACMI-approved for a high-quality, safe product you can trust. Whether you’re emphasizing text, or just feel like getting creative, choose BIC Brite Liner Highlighters.

Organization Gets Trendy BIC Brite Liner Grip Pastel Highlighters emphasize what’s important on the page without obscuring the text below. Resists Drying Out These highlighters can resist drying out for up to eight hours without a cap, so you can work with confidence. BIC Brite Liner Highlighters are great for use in homes, schools, and offices alike. *When the cap is left off for 8 hours.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 3, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great colors great value !
reviews.reviewText: I like the colors available and they don’t bleed. The grips that they have are a nice touch and for the value you get a lot. These were pretty cheap and the quality is actually good there is no downsides really

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 17, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very minimal bleed-through
reviews.reviewText: I use a ton of highlighters, especially in my Bible but with those delicate pages I have to be careful of bleed-through.I ordered this box of Bic highlighters mainly because I liked the colors & they were a good price. It was my first time trying them so I wasn’t sure if I would like them or not. My only regret is not ordering multiple boxes. The colors are great, vibrant enough to see but still light enough to easily read what you’ve highlighted. They don’t bleed-through too much (so far it’s mainly just purple for me & only at the beginning & end), easy & comfortable to hold + they last a while. Definitely a good value, especially if you AREN’T using them on super thin bible pages

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 9, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Affordable and Perfect Pastel Colors
reviews.reviewText: All the colors are nice, if anything the purple may be darker than my liking. The highlighters are super affordable, have a nice pigment, and seem like they will last. No complaints! 5/5

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 27, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great colors and quality
reviews.reviewText: I really like these highlighters. I wanted something different than the bright traditional colors and these are perfect. Usually purple highlighters are too dark and yellow highlighters are a bit obnoxious to look at, these are eye catching and soft which I appreciate. Bic quality is also up to par. One of the highlighters came with a rip in the grip but there’s 12 in the pack and the rest were perfectly fine.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 6, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Its the perfect basic higlighter!
reviews.reviewText: What's not to like? The colors are perfect, no bleeding even through the thinnest paper. You can erase things underneath the highlight, and it still looks good! They are amazing especially for the price point. I definitely recommend getting the big box like I did however, because they seem to grow legs and walk away! I really like that they wont dry up either. I've used many highlighters and I think these are my favorite simply because of how basic they are and how nicely they stick out on paper.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 30, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Very nice but the purple is too dark for light pencils!!
reviews.reviewText: I love these pastel highlighters so much, the coral is my favorite color although it's a bit too close to the pink so I have to be a little careful with using the two together.My biggest complaint is that I primarily use these on pencils and the purple feel pretty dark compared to the other shades!!If you write dark or use a pen it's probably not an issue but I write small and apply medium (?) amount of pressure with my 0.5 lead so it's a little annoying to use.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 9, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I really like these. I have not used them long enough to say how quickly they dry out. But, they seem durable and work well. They are light enough to see through well and they are cute colors

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 6, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Smooth, Great Colors. Doesn’t bleed UNLESS you push the highlighters down. So just use them lightly and the pigment will print just as intended.

I love these pastel highlighter colors! I'm not a big fan of the bright neon colors that are typically sold, so I gravitated towards these. They are not light enough to read through and not super dark, but can be extra saturated on some papers. Will sometimes seep through, depending if the paper is thin or not. But I haven't experienced it bleeding onto the next page.Super cute and will be sticking with these for a long time!
Love my Bic highlighters. You get a great quantity as well as great quality and they're darn cute colours for school and my daily planner/journal.

Got on sale, was a good price for them. All work, no duds! Very bright yellow(as this is a yellow highlighter so that’s expected..). They last an average amount of time. I go through about 1 highlighter every 2-3 weeks(I do a lot of highlighting, daily, for work).

Los marcadores no traspasan la hoja, solo por la última gota de tinta que queda cuando despegas el marcador pero puede retirarse cuando todavía está fresco.Pintan bastante bien.El color azul es más como un tono Cyan pero aún así está muy bonito el color.
I use them so much I think I’m on my 4th pack haha. They do last long I just use mine everyday. Beautiful colours
